ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectCanada-Square Kilometre Array Observatory concerning the Accession of Canada ** AGREEMENT **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to BRING INTO FORCE for Canada the AGREEMENT between Canada and the Square Kilometre Array Observatory concerning the ACCESSION OF CANADA TO THE CONVENTION ESTABLISHING THE SQUARE KILOMETRE ARRAY OBSERVATORY, done at Ottawa on October 13, 2023 and at Lower Withington, United Kingdom, on October 30, 2023.
